1
00:00:09,030 --> 00:00:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for bringing me that message from 
Cecilia even on your day off, Teal.</font>

2
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, don't worry about me.</font>

3
00:00:16,030 --> 00:00:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to visit the guardian 
deity, and it was on my way.</font>

4
00:00:19,330 --> 00:00:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... see.</font>

5
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'm gonna go. Get some rest.</font>

6
00:00:24,040 --> 00:00:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care out there.</font>

7
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Teal was acting awfully docile.</i></font>

8
00:00:31,090 --> 00:00:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my guardian deity!</font>

9
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I stayed respectful of the time and place</font>

10
00:00:37,010 --> 00:00:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and controlled myself, just like you said!</font>

11
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get all excited! 
You'll collapse again!</font>

12
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look! I have some of the 
magicite you love so much!</font>

13
00:00:46,810 --> 00:00:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You found such fine ore for me?</font>

14
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll work my very hardest,</font>

15
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so please eat all you like! 
Don't hold back!</font>

16
00:00:54,340 --> 00:00:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to think carefully 
about what you just said.</font>

17
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Gar's basically just a 
gigolo at this point, huh?</font>

18
00:01:05,990 --> 00:01:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mustn't laugh.</font>

19
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's clear how much Teal 
genuinely loves Gar, isn't it?</font>

20
00:01:16,130 --> 00:01:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki?</font>

21
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... This tea's really good.</font>

22
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe all my practice 
is starting to pay off.</font>

23
00:01:29,970 --> 00:01:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today was fun, as always...</i></font>

24
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but do I really want 
things to stay this way?</i></font>

25
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

26
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why did you call <i>me</i> over for this?</font>

27
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no one else I can 
turn to for love advice!</font>

28
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please!</font>

29
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Captain... you have 
no friends, after all.</font>

30
00:03:22,450 --> 00:03:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rude! I have friends!</font>

31
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? What did you do this time?</font>

32
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I just want some love advice!</font>

33
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, you know how I can use Vanish 
Wave to turn invisible, right?</font>

34
00:03:38,090 --> 00:03:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So after saying goodbye to Cecilia,</font>

35
00:03:40,070 --> 00:03:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wondering what she 
might be doing, so...</font>

36
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good enough!</font>

37
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not done yet!</font>

38
00:03:55,790 --> 00:04:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">I had no idea Cecilia was 
putting in that much effort.</font></font>

39
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that made me worry that maybe</font>

40
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really don't know the girl 
I love that well at all.</font>

41
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's incredibly creepy.</font>

42
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

43
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I arrest you for unlawful 
entry and stalking?</font>

44
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just came here for some love advice!</font>

45
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear...</font>

46
00:04:20,020 --> 00:04:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I don't think things 
are going too badly.</font>

47
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But for all your hollering 
that you love Cecilia so much,</font>

48
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're not aggressive enough!</font>

49
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From my perspective, you're a coward!</font>

50
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?!</font>

51
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you just want to be her 
teatime companion forever?</font>

52
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well...</font>

53
00:04:39,770 --> 00:04:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't make any progress if you 
barely know anything about her.</font>

54
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true...</font>

55
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Duke.</font>

56
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just one thing:</font>

57
00:04:50,810 --> 00:04:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't be a stalker.</font>

58
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

59
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A stalker?</font>

60
00:04:57,230 --> 00:05:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... are you actually a 
criminal, not an ordinary civilian?</font>

61
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, no, it's not like that...</font>

62
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:06,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You showed up at just the right time.</font>

63
00:05:06,820 --> 00:05:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving the rest to someone 
who knows Cecilia well.</font>

64
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

65
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-So...</font>

66
00:05:17,130 --> 00:05:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me everything 
you know about Cecilia.</font>

67
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross. Zero points.</font>

68
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DUKE ASKED ME TO COME.</font>

69
00:05:23,970 --> 00:05:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, would you just use your voice?</font>

70
00:05:27,210 --> 00:05:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were talking last time.</font>

71
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"No. That was a special exception."</font>

72
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NO. THAT WAS A SPECIAL EXCEPTION.</font>

73
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, I'm sorry, okay?!</font>

74
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I guess I can't make you 
talk if you don't want to.</font>

75
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, you want to know about Cecilia?</font>

76
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do owe you for the advice 
you gave me before,</font>

77
00:05:47,860 --> 00:05:49,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'll tell you.</font>

78
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do!</font>

79
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's see...</font>

80
00:05:53,410 --> 00:05:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think the hero's party 
would exist without Cecilia.</font>

81
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you guys get hurt that often?</font>

82
00:06:00,850 --> 00:06:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I mean. But first...</font>

83
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's the problem of all 
the women who flock to Yuga.</font>

84
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi!</font>

85
00:06:09,470 --> 00:06:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}CHILL OUT.</font>

86
00:06:09,470 --> 00:06:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The swordsman's written 
notes didn't stop them,</font>

87
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cut it out already!</font>

88
00:06:12,210 --> 00:06:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and when I stepped in, things 
just got more heated.</font>

89
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Move it!</font>

90
00:06:17,090 --> 00:06:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Out of our way!</font>

91
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, please calm down.</font>

92
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Cecilia always calmed 
the storm for us.</font>

93
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"She did almost all of 
the background work."</font>

94
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, you should all be sharing that.</font>

95
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-We do things when we can!</font>

96
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}WE DIVIDED UP THE TASKS WE COULD DIVIDE UP.
I WAS THE COOK.</font>

97
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"We divided up the tasks 
we could divide up.</font>

98
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was the cook." Really?</font>

99
00:06:42,210 --> 00:06:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you know I can't cook!</font>

100
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what about Yuga?</font>

101
00:06:48,010 --> 00:06:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can, but whenever he goes 
out to gather ingredients,</font>

102
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he always finds trouble to get into.</font>

103
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia and I were in 
charge of gathering intel.</font>

104
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since our swordsman's so useless, y'know.</font>

105
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia managed our money, too.</font>

106
00:07:06,010 --> 00:07:08,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Yuga contributed nothing at all?!</font>

107
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe not, but the incidents he caused</font>

108
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">always ended up helping someone somehow.</font>

109
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad Yuga was our hero.</font>

110
00:07:21,970 --> 00:07:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His kindness is the real deal.</font>

111
00:07:27,010 --> 00:07:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I feel like I understand 
Yuga a little better now.</font>

112
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's <i>not </i>what I want! 
I was asking about Cecilia!</font>

113
00:07:38,670 --> 00:07:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was there anything else?</font>

114
00:07:42,090 --> 00:07:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. She had that nickname.</font>

115
00:07:44,610 --> 00:07:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What nickname?</font>

116
00:07:45,830 --> 00:07:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know? Oh, it was brilliant!</font>

117
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia was...</font>

118
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be having a fun conversation.</font>

119
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia?!</font>

120
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

121
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was looking for you, Mikana. 
I wanted to talk to you.</font>

122
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were just... talking 
about old memories...</font>

123
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to talk about old 
memories with you, too.</font>

124
00:08:07,970 --> 00:08:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At <i>length</i>, I assure you.</font>

125
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, Raven,</font>

126
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll be taking our leave for today.</font>

127
00:08:16,350 --> 00:08:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

128
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why only me?!</font>

129
00:08:22,910 --> 00:08:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, I'm sorry, but it's not my 
place to tell you Cecilia's nickname.</font>

130
00:08:28,970 --> 00:08:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's okay.</font>

131
00:08:30,730 --> 00:08:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikana's noble sacrifice taught 
me one of Cecilia's landmines.</font>

132
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, do you still have some time?</font>

133
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the orphanage where Cecilia 
does a lot of volunteer work.</font>

134
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

135
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! It's the Cold-blooded Swordsman!</font>

136
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cold-blooded Swordsman!</font>

137
00:08:54,050 --> 00:08:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cold-blooded Swordsman?</font>

138
00:08:55,450 --> 00:08:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THAT'S MY NICKNAME.</font>

139
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah.</font>

140
00:08:58,050 --> 00:09:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cold-blooded Swordsman!</font>

141
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has no blood or tears!</font>

142
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:05,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys don't even know 
what that expression means.</font>

143
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, where's the Holy Mother?</font>

144
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Mother?</font>

145
00:09:09,060 --> 00:09:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't the Holy Mother coming today?</font>

146
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna eat the Holy Mother's desserts!</font>

147
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Cold-blooded Swordsman!</font>

148
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:23,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I don't speak when I fight,</font>

149
00:09:23,850 --> 00:09:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">people seem to see me as a cold-blooded 
man who sheds no blood or tears.</font>

150
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's why you're the 
Cold-blooded Swordsman.</font>

151
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuga's nickname is "the Wandering Hero."</font>

152
00:09:36,140 --> 00:09:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikana's is "the Guardian," 
or "the Eternal Friend."</font>

153
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm kinda curious
where those came from...</font>

154
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:44,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Cecilia...</font>

155
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why doesn't she like being 
called the Holy Mother?</font>

156
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not my place to tell you.</font>

157
00:09:51,070 --> 00:09:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you can just learn 
more about it from now on.</font>

158
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you'll have opportunities.</font>

159
00:09:56,310 --> 00:09:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess so.</font>

160
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you don't know what 
to do once you find out...</font>

161
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind. Anyway, what 
are you going to do now?</font>

162
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's the question, huh?</font>

163
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be best if I could get to know 
Cecilia better and get closer to her...</font>

164
00:10:17,330 --> 00:10:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you take on a quest with her?</font>

165
00:10:19,810 --> 00:10:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean... thanks to you, I...</font>

166
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it!</font>

167
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the heroine is in a tight spot, 
the protagonist gallantly saves her!</font>

168
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And from there, love is inevitably born!</font>

169
00:10:35,050 --> 00:10:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Operation I'm a Protagonist, 
Too" begins now!</font>

170
00:10:43,190 --> 00:10:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to get Cecilia to agree.</font>

171
00:10:47,090 --> 00:10:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today's the day I show her what I can do!</font>

172
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then...</font>

173
00:10:50,890 --> 00:10:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

174
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:58,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are <i>you</i> here?</font>

175
00:10:58,150 --> 00:11:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The swordsman asked me to accompany you.</font>

176
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something else came up, apparently.</font>

177
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raven!</font>

178
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what are we doing?</font>

179
00:11:07,220 --> 00:11:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to show Cecilia 
what you can do, right?</font>

180
00:11:09,730 --> 00:11:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do have a plan.</font>

181
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hear it. I'll score it for you.</font>

182
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Score it?</font>

183
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The quest is to get rid of some undead 
that have made their den in a mansion.</font>

184
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll be a great chance 
for Cecilia to shine.</font>

185
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

186
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, won't it?</font>

187
00:11:26,570 --> 00:11:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I was thinking...</font>

188
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave this to me!</font>

189
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, you're the best!</font>

190
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... my dream was that I'd mow 
down all the undead myself...</font>

191
00:11:40,730 --> 00:11:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirty points.</font>

192
00:11:42,260 --> 00:11:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harsh!</font>

193
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you <i>dumb</i>?! Cecilia is a <i>priestess</i>!</font>

194
00:11:47,570 --> 00:11:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dealing with undead is her specialty!</font>

195
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

196
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your problem is that you base 
all your plans around yourself!</font>

197
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your priority should be 
what Cecilia will think!</font>

198
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry...</font>

199
00:12:01,570 --> 00:12:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you and Cecilia can 
be the main fighters today.</font>

200
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be on support.</font>

201
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two need to work together 
to defeat the enemy.</font>

202
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to form a relationship 
of trust, don't you?</font>

203
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I get it. I think I can do that.</font>

204
00:12:17,050 --> 00:12:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting.</font>

205
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Mikana?</font>

206
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be tagging along on this quest.</font>

207
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's very reassuring!</font>

208
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I brought someone else, too.</font>

209
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happiness!</font>

210
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi.</font>

211
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your help the other day.</font>

212
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

213
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, shall we get going?</font>

214
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it.</font>

215
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Let's take out those undead!</font>

216
00:12:46,890 --> 00:12:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay.</font>

217
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it right there!</font>

218
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you forget the plan already?</font>

219
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah!</font>

220
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So anyway, Cecilia and I 
will take the front line.</font>

221
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikana and Happiness, you're 
the rear guard. Okay?</font>

222
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's not giving the slightest 
hint of being afraid of ghosts.</i></font>

223
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess that's to be expected.</i></font>

224
00:13:16,650 --> 00:13:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there they are already.</font>

225
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Circle!</font>

226
00:13:27,310 --> 00:13:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that was quick.</font>

227
00:13:29,460 --> 00:13:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Cecilia for you.</font>

228
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take these.</font>

229
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Circle!</font>

230
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you tired, Cecilia?</font>

231
00:13:52,430 --> 00:13:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just fine.</font>

232
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Circle is an essential 
spell for any priest.</font>

233
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've boosted my magic efficiency for it.</font>

234
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

235
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's still a good idea 
to stay hydrated, though.</font>

236
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

237
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was thoughtful.</font>

238
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our captain is like that.</font>

239
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess he's the type to 
take off in weird directions</font>

240
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when he overthinks things.</font>

241
00:14:18,950 --> 00:14:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the last room.</font>

242
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never see this many undead 
packed into such a small space.</font>

243
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's clear they have a leader.</font>

244
00:14:27,950 --> 00:14:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words...</font>

245
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is where we'll find the boss.</font>

246
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

247
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">an Undead King.</font>

248
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure looks important with 
that crown on its head.</font>

249
00:14:49,190 --> 00:14:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they strong?</font>

250
00:14:50,410 --> 00:14:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An Undead King's strength isn't much 
different from that of normal undead.</font>

251
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just have a bit more intelligence.</font>

252
00:14:58,830 --> 00:14:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wimp.</font>

253
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't live up to 
its name at all, then.</font>

254
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, dead one who has taken up 
residence in someone else's house</font>

255
00:15:07,810 --> 00:15:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without consent!</font>

256
00:15:09,620 --> 00:15:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will return you to the afterlife!</font>

257
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pathetic.</font>

258
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just who are you people?</font>

259
00:15:17,490 --> 00:15:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! We have intruders!</font>

260
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your buddies won't be coming.</font>

261
00:15:22,410 --> 00:15:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

262
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only undead left in here is you!</font>

263
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you're just an ordinary skeleton!</font>

264
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

265
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki...</font>

266
00:16:00,450 --> 00:16:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are...</font>

267
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...scum.</font>

268
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, uh... It was just a little prank...</font>

269
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fiend.</font>

270
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again, I didn't—</font>

271
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brute.</font>

272
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a chance to explain myself!</font>

273
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you... How dare you...</font>

274
00:16:16,830 --> 00:16:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you?! How dare you?! 
How dare you?! How dare you?!</font>

275
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, okay?!</font>

276
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

277
00:16:29,350 --> 00:16:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about this one?!</font>

278
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lose.</font>

279
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How very honorable of you.</font>

280
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You won't resist anymore?</font>

281
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've lost.</font>

282
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have lost.</font>

283
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia, it sounds like 
he's resigned himself.</font>

284
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use Holy Circle to put 
a quick end to this.</font>

285
00:17:06,650 --> 00:17:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so attached to that crown?</font>

286
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This crown was important to me.</font>

287
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know why.</font>

288
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was just very important.</font>

289
00:17:17,390 --> 00:17:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was important to you?</font>

290
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you were the king of some 
nation when you were alive.</font>

291
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

292
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll send you to the afterlife 
along with your crown.</font>

293
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way she's handling this...</i></font>

294
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heaven's Rondo.</font>

295
00:17:57,090 --> 00:17:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel so nostalgic...</font>

296
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear a voice.</font>

297
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The voice of...</font>

298
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia! You shouldn't 
use such advanced magic!</font>

299
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we've gotten rid of all the undead.</font>

300
00:18:14,930 --> 00:18:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's mission complete.</font>

301
00:18:17,210 --> 00:18:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. Shall we go home, then?</font>

302
00:18:20,150 --> 00:18:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Mikana and Happiness, since 
you didn't do any work here,</font>

303
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why don't you go check around the mansion?</font>

304
00:18:26,890 --> 00:18:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, fine!</font>

305
00:18:28,670 --> 00:18:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll work.</font>

306
00:18:30,110 --> 00:18:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll meet back at the carriage.</font>

307
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Cecilia, can I lend you my shoulder?</font>

308
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or carry you on my back?</font>

309
00:18:40,420 --> 00:18:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry...</font>

310
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take that shoulder.</font>

311
00:18:46,890 --> 00:18:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used too much magic, huh?</font>

312
00:18:50,910 --> 00:18:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't sure if he'd be able 
to take his crown with him.</font>

313
00:18:55,450 --> 00:18:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sure looked happy, though.</font>

314
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like she can't make it.</i></font>

315
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki?!</font>

316
00:19:06,090 --> 00:19:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is embarrassing...</font>

317
00:19:09,210 --> 00:19:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

318
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll move as fast as I can so 
the other two don't see us.</font>

319
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why...</font>

320
00:19:26,850 --> 00:19:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you guys so far apart?</font>

321
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trouble?</font>

322
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is our stop.</font>

323
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Good work today.</font>

324
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye.</font>

325
00:19:43,810 --> 00:19:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? What's my score?</font>

326
00:19:46,370 --> 00:19:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you remembered, huh?</font>

327
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just tell me.</font>

328
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No score.</font>

329
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

330
00:19:56,750 --> 00:20:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I'm not going 
to score that one.</font>

331
00:20:00,610 --> 00:20:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! You mean it wasn't even scorable?!</font>

332
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not that.</font>

333
00:20:05,970 --> 00:20:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's for the best.</font>

334
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't overthink everything. Just 
do the best at what you can do.</font>

335
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds kinda noncommittal.</font>

336
00:20:17,220 --> 00:20:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. It's the 
best advice I can give.</font>

337
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm going home.</font>

338
00:20:25,270 --> 00:20:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Thanks for today.</font>

339
00:20:30,330 --> 00:20:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have to work hard, too.</font>

340
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way,</font>

341
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you visited the orphanage.</font>

342
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kids told me.</font>

343
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you found out my nickname, 
I have to ask you...</font>

344
00:20:52,390 --> 00:20:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't ever call me that.</font>

345
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:59,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure. I won't do 
anything you don't like.</font>

346
00:20:59,280 --> 00:21:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... can I ask why?</font>

347
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

348
00:21:04,890 --> 00:21:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, if you don't 
want to, that's fine.</font>

349
00:21:07,060 --> 00:21:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... it really suits you, I think.</font>

350
00:21:11,690 --> 00:21:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">The way you spoke to the Undead King... 
You just had this air of sanctity.</font></font>

351
00:21:17,770 --> 00:21:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It reminded me of that time 
in the Demon King's castle.</font>

352
00:21:20,210 --> 00:21:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, you really 
reminded me of a saint.</font>

353
00:21:23,470 --> 00:21:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I felt like a saint 
was reaching out to me.</font>

354
00:21:27,970 --> 00:21:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A... saint?</font>

355
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean... er...</font>

356
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

357
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you why they 
call me Holy Mother.</font>

358
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a famous story, so it's better than 
letting you hear it from someone else.</font>

359
00:21:51,100 --> 00:21:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so <i>amazing</i>, Cecilia!</font>

360
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're good at cooking and sewing,</font>

361
00:21:55,170 --> 00:21:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and at gathering intel and 
handling our money, too!</font>

362
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're...</font>

363
00:21:59,630 --> 00:22:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">just like a mom!</font>

364
00:22:04,850 --> 00:22:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From then on, he started calling me 
"Mom" in front of people all the time.</font>

365
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop laughing!</font>

366
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For crying out loud! I couldn't 
have a child as big as him!</font>

367
00:22:20,130 --> 00:22:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry...</font>

368
00:22:21,460 --> 00:22:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Yoki!</font>

